{"tid":2460830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐洲議會議長：歐洲不是沙包絕不能接受恐嚇，警告對中國採取反制行動","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:49:38.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e88cf7078aa3744a51573b1270181343e5dedd1","tid":2460830,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"中國制裁歐洲議會議員，激起抵制中歐投資協定聲浪高漲，重要黨團要求同意協定的前提是取消制裁，而歐洲議會議長更表示歐洲不是沙包絕不能接受恐嚇，並揚言對中國採取反制行動。<br />\n<br />\n而歐洲議會議長薩索里（David Sassoli）繼周一表示中國的決定是不可接受的，並且將產生後果後，周三他進一步表示歐洲不是中國的沙包，絕不能接受任何恐嚇，揚言對北京採取報復行動，但他未透露報復行動是否包括拒絕中歐投資協定。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會雖然目前許多議員發聲批評中國，但歐洲議會是由27成員國逾700位議員組成，中國透過重大建設等拉攏其中一些國家，再加上中國開放市場的商機潛力，使人關注歐洲議會是否會有實際行動。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟執委會完成中歐投資協定後，尚需經檢視協定文本以及翻譯成數十種歐盟語言文件，後再經歐盟27個成員國同意及歐洲議會的批准才會生效，整個過程預估在明年初才會走完。"},{"pid":"d367cde6e283eacedfadf063a7a2c364d51c9890","tid":2460830,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded10f5ea5a37fe37d1363d2f4d7d2a56b26d871","tid":2460830,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210325/3OMHDDMYK5FOTKNX5SG7UMIDSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210325%2F3OMHDDMYK5FOTKNX5SG7UMIDSA%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=75ebc40a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210325%2F3OMHDDMYK5FOTKNX5SG7UMIDSA%2F&h=18fce618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210325/3OMHDDMYK5FOTKNX5SG7UMIDSA/</a>"},{"pid":"ec084bd2d795741ae93efe6e6a6b8629e7dea202","tid":2460830,"uid":290118